<p class="">As I have said, for this action there is no precedent. There is no precedent for these attacks from the air, because aircraft were not previously developed. It gives rise to a series of new problems, as to which previous experience is not available.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
